## 🏗️ Architecture (Phase 1-4 Complete)

### Integrated Go-Zig Hybrid Kernel

```
┌───────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  🔷 Go Orchestrator (Dispatcher + Workers)            │
│  ├─ RingBuffer: Lock-free queue (15ns/op)            │
│  ├─ Dispatcher: Job routing (14.67 ns/op)            │
│  ├─ Backpressure: Flow control (0.3-0.8 ns/op)      │
│  └─ SHM Manager: Zero-copy memory (150-180 ns/op)   │
└───────────┬───────────────────────────────┬───────────┘
            │  10MB Shared Memory (SHM)     │
            │  Header: 128B (Cache-aligned) │
            │  Data: 10MB-128B              │
┌───────────▼───────────────────────────────▼───────────┐
│  🔶 Zig Kernel (Lock-Free Spin-Loop)                 │
│  ├─ State Machine: Idle→Writing→Ready→Reading       │
│  ├─ Atomic CAS: 10.99 ns/op (no mutexes)            │
│  ├─ SIMD Dispatcher:                                 │
│  │  ├─ MatMul 4×4 (Implemented)                      │
│  │  ├─ FFT-16 (Implemented)                          │
│  │  └─ Sum-Reduce (Implemented)                      │
│  └─ Zero-Copy Data Access (Read-Only)               │
└───────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

### Data Structure: EngineHeader (128 bytes)

```
Cache Line 1 (0-63 bytes):
  Magic          [0:8]      uint64  (0x47524945_00000001 = "GRIE")
  Version        [8:12]     uint32
  State          [12:16]    int32   (atomic: IDLE|WRITING|READY|READING)
  SeqNum         [16:24]    uint64  (atomic: sequence counter)
  Timestamp      [24:32]    int64   (Unix nanoseconds)
  DataLen        [32:40]    uint64  (actual payload size)
  Padding        [40:64]    24 bytes

Cache Line 2 (64-127 bytes):
  WriterPID      [64:72]    int64
  ReaderPID      [72:80]    int64
  TotalWrites    [80:88]    uint64  (atomic: cumulative writes)
  TotalReads     [88:96]    uint64  (atomic: cumulative reads)
  Padding        [96:128]   32 bytes
```

### State Machine (Lock-Free Protocol)

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                    State Transitions                      │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

[Go Writer]                         [Julia/Go Reader]
    │                                    │
    ├─→ IDLE (initial)                   │
    │    │                               │
    │    ├─→ CAS(IDLE, WRITING)          │
    │    │   (atomic acquire write)      │
    │    │                               │
    │    ├─→ Copy data to shared mem     │
    │    │                               │
    │    ├─→ UpdateSeqNum()              │
    │    │                               │
    │    ├─→ STORE(READY)                │
    │    │                               │
    │    └───────────────────────────┐   │
    │                                │   │
    │                                └──→├─→ Poll: LoadState()
    │                                    │   while State != READY
    │                                    │
    │                                    ├─→ CAS(READY, READING)
    │                                    │   (atomic acquire read)
    │                                    │
    │                                    ├─→ Copy data from shared mem
    │                                    │
    │                                    ├─→ UpdateTotalReads()
    │                                    │
    │                                    ├─→ STORE(IDLE)
    │                                    │
    │←───────────────────────────────────┤
    │
    └─→ IDLE (ready for next cycle)
```

